document_data.name: Sheh'stek
document_data.mainbody: '''Sheh'stek''' was a [[lizardfolk]] from the [[Vast Swamp]] in [[Cormyr]] in [[1479 DR]].
document_data.History: In 1479 DR, Sheh'stek was one of the lizardfolk that came through a ''[[portal]]'' in the Vast Swamp and arrived in [[Undermountain]]. He was sent to explore a portion of the dungeon and was captured by the [[vampire]] [[Dayan]]. Sheh'stek was left in his cell to die.
